Oh cool it makes a sandwich.

00:01:08.620 --> 00:01:10.490
Yup. All the details about how

00:01:10.489 --> 00:01:13.129
the black box actually makes the sandwich is not important.

00:01:13.129 --> 00:01:15.509
All you need to know is that it takes bread as an input.

00:01:15.510 --> 00:01:17.440
That's kind of like the functions we've been using.

